## Overview
The **Alliance for Justice (AFJ)** is a progressive advocacy organization founded in **1979**. It focuses on ensuring a fair and impartial judiciary, advancing justice and democracy, and safeguarding the rights of marginalized communities. The organization is best known for its work on judicial nominations, nonprofit advocacy, and policy reform.

